  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00028', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-114-d1d05825', 'sub-public-health-specialist-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某人在整個網絡内之位置特殊，若將其從網絡中移除，則原網絡會分裂成兩個以上的網絡。請問 以上敘述最符合下列那一項社會網絡特徵？', '["密度（density）", "同質性（homogeneity）", "中心性（centrality）", "結構洞（structuralhole）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "007e33ed379e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "37ad037b45e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "108", "s": "0806", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "健康社會行為學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00029', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-114-d1d05825', 'sub-public-health-specialist-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據生態模式（ecologicalmodel）之觀點，下列何者最不符合其核心原則？', '["健康行為受到個人、家庭、社區與政策等多層次因素之影響", "各層次因素之間可能會互相影響，產生交互作用", "改變健康行為最有效的方法是只針對個人層級進行介入", "應用生態模式設計介入時，應針對特定健康行為加以調整"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "007e33ed379e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "37ad037b45e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "108", "s": "0806", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "健康社會行為學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
